            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Filicausus"
                            >Filicaus</name></persName> vir venerabilis <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbiter</rs>
                        <foreign>si indirizza alla</foreign>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Cells/hermitages" ref="#juridical_persons/260"
                            >beatissimi Sancti Quirici</orgName>, sita in <geogName>fundo
                            Arno</geogName> ubi vocabulum est <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Oil #Acorns #Churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#places/746">vico Pontoni</placeName> prope <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers">Arme</placeName>. Filicaus, a paucis diebus <rs
                            key="#Venditio">conparationem</rs> feci de <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >aliquantula terrola</rs> prope ipsa sancta dei ecclesia beatissimi
                        Sancti Quirici, qui posita est (…) prope fluvio Arme in locum qui vocator
                        Pontoni, et <rs key="#Private_foundations">ibi edeficavi cellula</rs>, ubi
                        nunc havitare videor. <foreign>Ora dona alla chiesa di S. Quirico</foreign>
                        ipsa suprascripta terra cum <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">olivetis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Acorns">silvis</rs> (…), <foreign>riservandosene l’usufrutto
                            vitalizio; e riservandosi di scegliere la persona che vivrà dopo di lui
                            nella</foreign> cellula, <foreign>gestendone i beni</foreign>. Et iterum
                        meum complaceret animum de <persName key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales"><name
                                ref="Tanuara">Tanuara</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales">ancella dei</rs>, qui mecum est, si super me
                        vixeret, liceat ei sina aliqua taxxationem in ipsa <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">cella</rs> vivere et ad ipsa sancta Dei vertutem
                        serviendum. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Agibertus">Achipert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Luca</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: Filicausu
                        presviter (ss); + <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Cunicausus"
                                >Cunicaus</name></persName> germano ipsius; + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Filipertus">Filipert</name></persName> germano
                        ipsius; + <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gisbertus"
                            >Chispert</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Ghiselmus">Ghiselm</name></persName> testis; + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Sindifridus de Sclito"
                            >Sintifrid</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/633"
                            >Sclito</placeName> testis; <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Teuprandus">Teusprand</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Eliseus">Alisei</name></persName> testis;</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
